    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find a few minor cosmetic blemishes and light scratches consistent with regular use. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only minor wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a dependable choice for any buyer looking for a quality pre-owned car.",
